<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan> Muraher zu
                            <expan>Flügelsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, pfleger zu Kelheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der
                            <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die der <expan>Eberh<ex>art</ex></expan>
<expan>Ryed<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Nikel <expan>Griess<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        knecht, dem <expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        Meyr<expan>hof<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>mawtn<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
                        Kelheim, an das <expan>lantger<ex>icht</ex></expan> getan hab etc., das
                        haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und haben umb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen die
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> Nikel Griessen und
                                <expan>sein<ex>en</ex></expan> knecht
                            <expan>Eberh<ex>art</ex></expan> für uns besandt und fleissig mit im
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt, also daz der
                                <expan>Eberh<ex>art</ex></expan> uns
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat, er well
                            <expan>dies<ex>elbe</ex></expan> sein klag <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>lantger<ex>icht</ex></expan> yecz abtun und fallen
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>; und meynt <add>auch</add>, er well
                        recht gen dem <expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>Meyrhof<ex>er</ex></expan> bey ewch zu Kelheim
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> suchen und <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        also daz er sicherheit und gelegt darczu hab. <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>, <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Eberh<ex>art</ex></expan> umb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> fürdrung und guten
                            <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> in den sachen zu
                            <expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>, als etc. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan> Katherine. </ab>
</div>
